goals.question: What is the distribution of percentage of job count across different job types?

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax = sns.barplot(x="job", y="count", data=data, palette="Blues_d")
    ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90, ha="right")
    ax.set(xlabel='Job Type', ylabel='Count')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of job types in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    sns.lineplot(x='year', y='count', data=data)
    plt.title('How has the count of jobs changed over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['job', 'sex', 'count']]
    data = data.groupby(['job', 'sex']).sum().reset_index()
    data['percentage'] = data.groupby('job')['count'].apply(lambda x: x / x.sum() * 100)
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    sns.barplot(x="job", y="percentage", hue="sex", data=data)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.legend(title='Gender', loc='upper right')
    plt.title('What is the gender distribution across different job types?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='year', y='count', kde=True, ax=ax)
    ax.set_xlabel('Year')
    ax.set_ylabel('Job Count')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of job count across different years?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
